{"_response_info":{"status":"ok"},"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/hemianopia-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/hemianopia-and-driving","title":"Hemianopia and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T12:54:30+00:00","details":{"need_id":"2278","business_proposition":false,"description":"You must tell DVLA if you have hemianopia - download the correct form to let them know","language":"en","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> if you have hemianopia (hemianopsia).</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice help-notice\">\n<p>You can be fined up to £1,000 if you don’t tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> about a medical condition that affects your driving. If you’re involved in an accident, you may be prosecuted.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Car or motorcycle licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1 and send to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065620.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘V1 - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 253KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Bus, coach or lorry licence</h2>\n\n<p>You must tell <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. Fill in form V1V and send to <abbr title=\"Driver Vehicle and Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@motor/documents/digitalasset/dg_065275.pdf\" title=\"Download medical questionnaire\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘V1V - Confidential medical information’ (PDF, 261KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n","alternative_title":"Hemianopsia and driving"},"tags":[],"related":[{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/going-to-court-victim-witness.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/going-to-court-victim-witness","title":"Going to court as a victim or witness","format":"guide","updated_at":"2013-01-09T12:53:52+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/driving-if-disabled.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/driving-if-disabled","title":"Medical conditions, disabilities and driving","format":"guide","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:10:22+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/health-conditions-and-driving.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/health-conditions-and-driving","title":"Health conditions and driving","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:13:59+00:00"},{"id":"https://www.gov.uk/api/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/reapply-driving-licence-medical-condition","title":"Re-apply for a driving licence following a medical condition","format":"answer","updated_at":"2013-01-09T13:11:37+00:00"}]}